name: Saudi Arabian 777-368ER [HZ-AK28] RTO and Takeoff from Paine Field ᴴᴰ
description:
Now on Flickr: https://www.flickr.com/photos/dude8472productions/

A new airline for me! Here we have one of Saudia's many Boeing 777s at Paine Field taxiing, performing a rejected takeoff, and then taxiing back and taking to the skies. Sorry for the lack of activity/commenting. I've been busy these past few days. Enjoy the video!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
